{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/adding-a-default-option-in-switch-statements","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Dodavanje Podrazumevane Opcije u switch Iskazima","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U <code>switch</code> iskazu mozda necete navesti sve moguce vrednosti kao <code>case</code> grane. Umesto toga, mozete dodati <code>default</code> granu koja ce se izvrsiti ako nijedna <code>case</code> grana ne odgovara. Posmatrajte je kao poslednji <code>else</code> u <code>if/else</code> lancu.</p>\n<p><code>default</code> treba da bude poslednja grana.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">switch (num) {\n  case value1:\n    statement1;\n    break;\n  case value2:\n    statement2;\n    break;\n...\n  default:\n    defaultStatement;\n    break;\n}\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244de","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Napisite <code>switch</code> iskaz koji postavlja <code>answer</code> po sledecim pravilima:\n<code>a</code> - <code>apple</code>\n<code>b</code> - <code>bird</code>\n<code>c</code> - <code>cat</code>\n<code>default</code> - <code>stuff</code></p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16653,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/adding-a-default-option-in-switch-statements"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function switchOfStuff(val) {\n  let answer = \"\";\n  // Only change code below this line\n\n\n\n  // Only change code above this line\n  return answer;\n}\n\nswitchOfStuff(1);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>switchOfStuff(\"a\")</code> treba da vrati string <code>apple</code></p>","testString":"assert(switchOfStuff('a') === 'apple');"},{"text":"<p><code>switchOfStuff(\"b\")</code> treba da vrati string <code>bird</code></p>","testString":"assert(switchOfStuff('b') === 'bird');"},{"text":"<p><code>switchOfStuff(\"c\")</code> treba da vrati string <code>cat</code></p>","testString":"assert(switchOfStuff('c') === 'cat');"},{"text":"<p><code>switchOfStuff(\"d\")</code> treba da vrati string <code>stuff</code></p>","testString":"assert(switchOfStuff('d') === 'stuff');"},{"text":"<p><code>switchOfStuff(4)</code> treba da vrati string <code>stuff</code></p>","testString":"assert(switchOfStuff(4) === 'stuff');"},{"text":"<p>Ne treba da koristite <code>if</code> ili <code>else</code> iskaze</p>","testString":"assert(!/else/g.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)) || !/if/g.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)));"},{"text":"<p>Treba da koristite <code>default</code> granu</p>","testString":"assert(switchOfStuff('string-to-trigger-default-case') === 'stuff');"},{"text":"<p>Treba da imate najmanje 3 <code>break</code> naredbe</p>","testString":"assert(__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/break/g).length > 2);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-javascript","dashedName":"adding-a-default-option-in-switch-statements","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-javascript","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/multiple-identical-options-in-switch-statements","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/selecting-from-many-options-with-switch-statements","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244de","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum) {\n  if (endNum - startNum === 0) {\n    return [startNum];\n  } else {\n    const numbers = rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum - 1);\n    numbers.push(endNum);\n    return numbers;\n  }\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/adding-a-default-option-in-switch-statements"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}